#: faq_raster.xml:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"* coverages to be not necessarily rectangular (which is often the case of "
"raster coverage covering large extents. See the possible raster arrangements "
"in the documentation)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: faq_raster.xml:228
#, no-c-format
